description: [``botocore``] Adds support for searching global contacts using the ActiveRegions filter, and pagination support for ListSecurityProfileFlowModules and ListEntitySecurityProfiles.
[``botocore``] Update endpoint-rules client to latest version

[``botocore``] This change sets the KafkaConnect GovCloud FIPS and FIPS DualStack endpoints to use kafkaconnect instead of kafkaconnect-fips as the service name. This is done to match the Kafka endpoints.
